Package wt.meeting

Uses the wt.meeting.MeetingService to manage wt.meeting.Meetings of various MeetingTypes having wt.meeting.Agendas and producing wt.meeting.Minutes, in particular wt.meeting.MeetingCenterMeetings with their associated wt.meeting.MeetingCenterMeetingInfo (also see the wt.meeting.WebexOperationHelper).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    WebexUserInfoDelegate


    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false

    The purpose of this delegate is to allow customization of the way Webex account names and passwords are created and stored.

Package wt.meeting Description
